body:
Type: <b>Bug</b>

When Copilot executes a command with `&&`, it only waits until the part before `&&` is finished. But usually, the last part is the one that needs attention.

For example: `cd $WORKSPACE && npx run test`.

Extension version: 0.31.2025081401
